	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.windcraft.cn/?p=297" rel="bookmark">起床服大厅跑酷活动</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		
<p>活动介绍：好久没来整活拉！这次就来玩玩跑酷吧！</p>



<p>活动时间:北京时间2020.2.7 20:00准时开始</p>



<p>活动地点：风音服起床战争Bedwars大厅
输入/server bedwars到达服务器</p>



<p>参与方式：在活动开始前到达指定地点准备</p>



<p>奖励：参与奖 风音纪念品<strong>蝙蝠蛋</strong>x1</p>



<p>      第一名奖励<strong>游戏币</strong>x500</p>



<p>      前三名奖励<strong>钻石块</strong>x10个</p>



<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
玩家可以选择奖品至空岛服/生存服</p>



<p>      <strong>只能选1个服哦~</strong></p>



<p>祝大家玩的开心哦</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/X47Q@1XKMABR3DB47_NX-1024x532.png" alt="" class="wp-image-298" srcset="https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/X47Q@1XKMABR3DB47_NX-1024x532.png 1024w, https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/X47Q@1XKMABR3DB47_NX-300x156.png 300w, https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/X47Q@1XKMABR3DB47_NX-768x399.png 768w, https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/X47Q@1XKMABR3DB47_NX-1200x623.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /></figure>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
